import React from "react"; import "./DietaryIcon.css"; // Archivo CSS para estilos personalizados. const dietaryIcons = { // Restricciones Dietéticas vegetarian: "./icons/vegetarian.png", vegan: "./icons/vegan.png", pescatarian: "./icons/pescatarian.png", ketogenic: "./icons/keto.png", paleo: "./icons/paleo.png", primal: "/icons/primal.png", lowFODMAP: "/icons/low-fodmap.png", whole30: "/icons/whole30.png", highProtein: "/icons/high-protein.png", lowCarb: "/icons/low-carb.png", lowFat: "/icons/low-fat.png", sugarConscious: "/icons/sugar-conscious.png", // Intolerancias y Alérgenos glutenFree: "/icons/gluten-free.png", dairyFree: "/icons/dairy-free.png", eggFree: "/icons/egg-free.png", peanutFree: "/icons/peanut-free.png", treeNutFree: "/icons/tree-nut-free.png", soyFree: "/icons/soy-free.png", fishFree: "/icons/fish-free.png", shellfishFree: "/icons/shellfish-free.png", wheatFree: "/icons/wheat-free.png", sesameFree: "/icons/sesame-free.png", sulfiteFree: "/icons/sulfite-free.png", celeryFree: "/icons/celery-free.png", mustardFree: "/icons/mustard-free.png", lupinFree: "/icons/lupin-free.png", molluskFree: "/icons/mollusk-free.png", // Información Nutricional (representativa) calories: "/icons/calories.png", carbohydrates: "/icons/carbohydrates.png", proteins: "/icons/proteins.png", fats: "/icons/fats.png", cholesterol: "/icons/cholesterol.png", fiber: "/icons/fiber.png", sugar: "/icons/sugar.png", // Ícono genérico default: "/icons/default.png", }; const DietaryIcon = ({ diet }) => { const icon = dietaryIcons[diet] || dietaryIcons.default; // Ícono por defecto. return (
{diet}
); }; export default DietaryIcon;
